query:
SELECT
                    event_id as "event_id: _",
                    event_payload as "event_payload: _"
                FROM webhook_subscription_events
                    WHERE
                        (cast($1 as INT8) IS NULL or event_id > $1) AND
                        (cast($2 as INT8) IS NULL or event_id <= $2)
                    ORDER BY event_id ASC
